Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    assignment
    builds GUI of the main window; gets values through poperties class from properties file; gets SQL command through SQLQueries class; executes SQL commands through queries class
    connectDB
    loads MySQL or MS-SQL driver and set the connection to SQL Server; gets values through properties class from properties file
    csvExport
    generates a csv file from current jTable in assignment class and place file on choosen path of destination; gets jTable thorugh assignment class
    EncryptDecryptPass
    encrypts/decrypts password gets values from properties class
    FileChooser
    generates a file chooser window
    launcher
    choose which kind of query you want to see; sets view property
    Login
    first executable class of programm sets all values given by user and stores values through properties class in properties file; tries to connect to SQL server through connectDB class
    passcryptor
    crypts user password and stores crypted password in properties class; enrypt and decrypt methods are used in EncryptDecryptPass class
    properties
    stores all important values into properties file in src folder
    queries
    sets jTable model and executes SQL queries from SQLQueries class; gets values from properties class; sets SQL connection from connectDB class; execute SQL query through SQLQueries class; decrypts password through EncryptDecryptPass class
    SQLQueries
    returns String of SQL query syntax; gets values from poperties class
